Target Profile We seek Hindu families
who are firmly committed to retaining their saMskAra-s, knowledge (traditional &amp; modern) across generations;
who preferably &ldquo;do the math&rdquo; (web) and conclude that modern industrial society will not last, for the most part, beyond a few generations. They should agree with the settlement constitution. Particularly, they should be willing to (eventually) switch over to Sanskrit - atleast for formal communication. Of course, they should (gradually) learn the language of the surrounding people (eg.
